London-based South African singer Toya DeLazy, real name Latoya Buthelezi, and her wife Alison “Ally” Chaig are expecting a baby. Toya shared the exciting news of their pregnancy on social media, where she expressed how grateful she was for her bundle of joy. Toya and Ally tied the knot late in 2021 in an intimate celebration. Their union is yet to be celebrated sometime this year. The couple has been together for 10 years, and while Toya lived between SA and the UK for a while in their relationship, she is now based in the UK.  For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.